name: v2.1
body:
The new v2.1 release contains various fixes, table view for a more user-friendly experience, improved end-user messages on CRUD commands and failures and new commands that let you work with the latest Lenses 2.1.

[View all changes from the previous release](https://github.com/Landoop/lenses-go/compare/v2.0...v2.1) (for developers)

name: v2.0
body:
